title: Moving On Up
itunes:title: Moving On Up
description:
Today on the show we had Diamond from the group Crime Mobbs, where she spoke about new projects, old relationships and more. Also, we had Nipsey's father stop by where he spoke about the legacy of his son, and the controversy in Ethiopia and more. Also Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to the republicans who voted against making Junteenth a federal holiday.
